	•	“name the repeated state”
	•	“store it once”
	•	“build larger answers from smaller solved states”

Dry Run (Opt)

Show:
	•	base states first
	•	next state filled from previous ones
	•	memo hit replacing recursion branch

How to Draw (Opt)

Best template:
	•	state table
	•	arrows from dependencies
	•	fill order marked
	•	one small legend: what dp[i] or dp[i][j] means

Opt Complexity Vis.

Metaphor:
	•	state count × transition count
