8) How to storyboard by bucket

Now the practical part.

⸻

Bucket 1 — Strip / Pointer storyboard

Use for:
	•	sliding window
	•	two pointers
	•	prefix/suffix sweeps
	•	center expansion

Frame anatomy
	•	strip stays fixed
	•	moving pointers highlighted
	•	small side box for counts/sum/best
	•	invariant under strip

What counts as a frame event
	•	R expands
	•	L shrinks
	•	sum updated
	•	best range updated
	•	mid chosen
	•	left/right pointer moves

Best storyboard rhythm
	1.	setup pointers
	2.	move one pointer
	3.	detect validity/condition
	4.	move second pointer if needed
	5.	update answer

