15. The practical gold-standard template

Here is the strict template every serious pattern chapter should satisfy.

Pattern chapter template

1. Definition

What the family is.

2. Applicability

When it is valid.

3. Non-applicability

When it fails or is misleading.

4. Brute-force baseline

