Layer 8 — Proof requirements

This is where the atlas becomes intellectually serious.

Each family must say how it is usually proven.

Different families require different proof grammars:

Invariant proof

Needed for:
	•	windows
	•	two pointers
	•	binary search
	•	monotonic stack
