⸻

16.2 Interval-difference proof

For range queries.

Structure
	•	interval = cumulative(right) minus cumulative(before-left)
	•	therefore stored prefix states recover interval answer correctly

⸻

16.3 Equal/relation-on-prefix proof

For balance/modulo/hash variants.

