22. Diagnostic decision tree for new problems

Q1

Is the main waste repeated search for current best among changing active candidates?
	•	no -> maybe not heap
	•	yes -> continue

Q2

Do I need full order or just repeated top extraction?
	•	full order once -> sort may be enough
	•	repeated top extraction -> heap likely valid

Q3

What subtype is it?
	•	kth/top-k -> fixed-size or repeated extraction heap
	•	merge ordered streams -> merge-k-streams heap
	•	weighted frontier -> graph heap
	•	active interval/task set -> scheduling heap

That is the operational diagnostic.

