	•	yes -> continue

Q2

Do components change mainly by merges/unions?
	•	no -> DSU may not fit
	•	yes -> continue

Q3

Do I only need representative-level facts (same set? count? root metadata)?
	•	no -> traversal/path methods may be needed
	•	yes -> DSU likely valid

Q4

What subtype is it?
	•	plain connectivity
	•	cycle/redundancy detection
	•	entity merge
	•	grid activation
	•	sorted-edge helper (Kruskal)

That is the operational diagnostic.

