Failure 1 — Choosing complex structure when prefix sums suffice

Overengineering.

Failure 2 — Choosing static structure when updates exist

Conceptual mismatch.

Failure 3 — Wrong combine rule

Fatal.

Failure 4 — Wrong interval coverage

Common segment-tree bug.

Failure 5 — Lazy propagation errors

