25. Final deep compression of the family

The irreducible statement of SQL / Relational is:

SQL / Relational is valid when the problem’s true structure is row relationships, grouping, or partitioned comparison, so procedural row-by-row logic can be collapsed into declarative relation transformations.

And the irreducible teaching statement is:

The learner has mastered SQL / Relational only when they can name:
