The best final schema is:

type LeetCodeVisualizerProblem = {
  meta: ProblemMeta;
  taxonomy: ProblemTaxonomy;
  buckets: ProblemBuckets;
  visuals: VisualSchema;
  testCases: TestCase[];
  solutions: SolutionSchema;
  traces: TraceSchema;
  ui: UiSchema;
};


