Here’s the master phases of solving LeetCode Q1–Q10, in-depth.

I’ll use the same solve lifecycle for each:
	1.	Problem intake
	2.	Surface translation
	3.	Input/output anatomy
	4.	Constraint reading
	5.	Brute-force construction
	6.	Waste diagnosis
	7.	Compression insight
