	•	if true -> enter body
	•	after body finishes -> 6(c) increment
	•	then go back to 6(b)

So the real control flow is:

6(a) -> 6(b) -> body -> 6(c) -> 6(b) -> body -> 6(c) -> ...

When condition becomes false:
	•	loop exits immediately
	•	body does not run again
	•	increment does not run again

