So how to prompt this methodology or approach or how to define it


Define it as a Micro-Step Code Execution Methodology.

That name is clean and precise.

What it is

It is a way to explain code by breaking each line into:
	•	line-level execution
	•	sub-step execution
	•	control-flow execution
	•	state updates
	•	early exits

So instead of saying:
	•	“line 6 runs”

you say:
	•	6(a) initialization
	•	6(b) condition check
	•	6(c) increment

and for expressions:
	•	8(a) read target
	•	8(b) read current_value
	•	8(c) compute subtraction
	•	8(d) assign needed_value

That is the methodology.

Best definition

Short definition

Micro-Step Code Execution Methodology = a code-sync dry-run system that decomposes each source line into ordered execution sub-steps and explains how control flow, state, memory, and return behavior evolve.

Even shorter

A code-synchronized operational dry run.

