7. BFS

Examples:
	•	shortest path unweighted
	•	rotting oranges

Memory delta count

Medium

Typical deltas
	•	enqueue
	•	dequeue
	•	mark visited
	•	distance/time set

Delta style
	•	dequeue node 4
	•	+ visited[7] = true
	•	enqueue node 7

