8. DFS / Backtracking

Examples:
	•	subsets
	•	permutations
	•	word search

Memory delta count

High in path-state terms

Typical deltas
	•	path push
	•	visited mark
	•	recursive enter
	•	recursive exit
	•	path pop
	•	visited unmark

Delta style
	•	path.push(3)
