Hashing	sparse, keyed, lookup-heavy	0–2	grow / overwrite	mostly permanent	insert, update, erase	map/set entries, counts, last-seen indices	side hash-map box + key highlights
Sliding window	oscillating, expand/shrink	1–4	grow and shrink	permanent per move, but window state oscillates	increment, decrement, insert, erase, pointer move	left/right pointers, freq map, validity counters	array strip + shaded window + freq panel
Two pointers	light, movement-driven	0–2	pointer motion	permanent	pointer move, swap, write	left/right/slow/fast pointers, occasional array swap	strip + pointer arrows
Monotonic stack	bursty	1–6+	prune then grow	permanent	push, pop	stack of indices/values	strip/histogram + stack panel
Monotonic deque	bursty with expiry	1–8+	prune / expire / grow	permanent	push back, pop back, pop front	deque of candidate indices	strip + deque panel with stale markers
Heap / priority queue	churn around frontier top	1–4	grow / shrink	mostly permanent, sometimes lazy-stale	push, pop, discard stale	heap contents, top element	heap panel + frontier list
