Backtracking	choose / recurse / unchoose	2–6+	grow then undo	highly reversible	push, pop, mark, unmark, place, remove	path, used flags, board placements	decision tree + path stack + undo arrows
DP table	monotone fill	1–3	grow knowledge	permanent	write cell, improve cell	dp array/table/memo entries	table/grid with newly filled cells
Prefix sum / cumulative state	steady cumulative + side updates	1–3	grow / overwrite	permanent	scalar update, map count update	prefix scalar, count map	strip + running prefix + side map
Graph advanced (Dijkstra / topo / relax)	compound	2–6+	improve / unlock / frontier move	mostly permanent improvements	relax, update parent, indegree decrement, push/pop	dist, parent, indegree, frontier	graph + frontier + metadata tables
DSU / Union-Find	sparse but impactful	1–4	merge / compress	permanent	parent rewrite, rank/size update	parent array, size/rank arrays	forest / representative table
Trie build	front-loaded growth	1–3	grow	permanent	create node, add child link, mark terminal	trie nodes and child edges	prefix tree growth
Trie query	mostly read-only	0–1	none / rare flag update	permanent if update exists	traverse, maybe mark	current node/path	prefix path highlight
Linked-list manipulation	local rewiring	1–5	relink	permanent	next change, prev change, attach, detach	pointers/links	node chain + pointer rewires
