Best practical rule

For every step in any pattern, first classify it into one of 4 buckets:
	1.	Read-only
	2.	Single mutation
	3.	Compound mutation
	4.	Reversible mutation

Then apply the exact delta type.

That keeps the system manageable even across many LeetCode patterns.

