A mature designer thinks:
what proof shape fits this design?

If state depends on smaller solved states

Use induction

If making local optimal choice

Use exchange argument

If discarding dominated cases

Use contradiction or monotonicity

If exploring all legal branches

Use exhaustive-search correctness

If using shortest frontier

Use layer/finalization proof

Design and proof should fit together naturally.

