Dominant repeated event

What gets repeated in brute force?

Optimization mechanism

What structure removes the repeated work?

Effective event count

How many optimized events remain?

Per-event cost

What is the cost of one optimized event?

Total runtime

Multiply them.

Growth class
	•	O(1)
	•	O(log n)
	•	O(n)
	•	O(n log n)
	•	O(n²)
	•	O(n³)
	•	O(n·target)
	•	O(2^n)
	•	O(n!)
