Short, tight, scalar-focused.

⸻

B. Hashing implementation

Examples:
	•	Two Sum
	•	longest substring
	•	frequency count
	•	prefix count map

Main implementation objects
	•	unordered_map
	•	unordered_set
	•	key/payload design

Main coding tasks
