	•	choose correct payload
	•	choose lookup-before-update or update-before-lookup
	•	handle duplicates correctly

Common bugs
	•	storing wrong payload
	•	losing earliest vs latest occurrence meaning
	•	using [] when find is safer
	•	duplicate mishandling

