12. Backtracking approach

Meaning

Make a choice, recurse, then undo it and try another.

Common structure
	•	choose
	•	recurse
	•	unchoose

Examples
	•	subsets
	•	permutations
	•	N-Queens
	•	combination sum
	•	word search

Strength
	•	natural for enumeration and constraint search
