Which type of step table for all leetcode question 



There is no single step-table type for all LeetCode questions.

The right answer is:

each LeetCode question belongs to one or more step-table families, and you choose the table based on the problem’s state evolution.

So the real question is:
	•	what is the main unit of progress?
	•	what is the main state representation?
	•	what is the main operation per step?

From that, you pick the step table.

