7. Best universal fallback

If you are unsure which step table to use, choose in this order:
	1.	micro-step code execution table if the goal is code-tracing
	2.	state-fill / recursion / frontier table depending on algorithm family
	3.	proof-invariant helper table if correctness is hard to see

So the fallback is not one table, but:
	•	one algorithm-family table
	•	plus optional micro-step support

