For all LeetCode questions, the correct step table type is chosen by the algorithm family:
	•	scan problems -> scalar scan
	•	cumulative problems -> prefix summary
	•	hashing problems -> hashmap-cache
	•	window problems -> sliding window
	•	pointer-boundary problems -> two-pointer boundary
	•	monotonic problems -> monotonic stack/deque
	•	priority/frontier problems -> heap-frontier
	•	unweighted graph traversal -> BFS layer
	•	recursive traversal -> DFS recursion
	•	choice-tree problems -> backtracking branch
	•	tabulation problems -> DP state-fill
	•	range subproblem problems -> interval DP
