When analyzing a linked question, ask:

Surface question

What does the problem say?

Logical object

Sequence? hierarchy? graph?

Link meaning

What does each pointer/reference mean?

Active topology

What is connected right now?

Mutation goal

What link pattern should exist after the algorithm?

Safe local rewrite

Which links must be saved before rewriting?

That is the right methodology.

