7. Optimized input -> state mapping

Instead of mapping input to all pairs, map input to:

processed prefix + complement lookup state

State form:

current index i
current value nums[i]
needed value = target - nums[i]
seen map = {value -> index}

So the optimized mapping is:

input
  ↓
stream of values
  ↓
for each value:
    compute needed complement
    query seen-prefix map
  ↓
if hit -> output pair
else -> extend seen-prefix map


