11. Universal function mapping

Main function form

(nums, target)
   ↓
scan each value x in nums
   ↓
compute need = target - x
   ↓
lookup need in seen map
   ├─ hit  -> return answer
   └─ miss -> store current value

So the core function family is:
	•	scan/update
	•	derive complement
	•	lookup
	•	conditional return
	•	insert

